# Monolith AI-Native Engineering Platform

Monorepo template for the Monolith platform. Modular rules in `.cursor/rules/` — read the relevant file before changing code.

## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|------------|
| Monorepo | Turborepo + pnpm workspaces |
| Web | Next.js 15, React 19, Tailwind 4, shadcn/ui (`@monolith/ui`) |
| API | NestJS 11, Prisma, PostgreSQL |
| Cache/queues | Redis, BullMQ |
| Mobile | Expo (`apps/mobile`) |
| Tests | Vitest, Playwright |
| Local | Docker Compose (`postgres`, `redis`, optional `api`/`web`) |
| Deploy | Vercel (web), Railway (api), Supabase (db), Upstash (redis) |

## Rule map

| Rule file | When to apply |
|-----------|----------------|
| `agent-behaviour.mdc` | Always — AI workflow and scope |
| `architecture.mdc` | Layers, modules, dependency boundaries |
| `backend.mdc` | `apps/api`, Prisma, queues |
| `frontend.mdc` | `apps/web`, `@monolith/ui` |
| `api-design.mdc` | HTTP contracts, DTOs, `@monolith/types` |
| `naming.mdc` | Files, symbols, env, DB names |
| `monorepo.mdc` | pnpm, Turbo, workspace packages |
| `testing.mdc` | Vitest, Playwright |
| `docker.mdc` | Compose, Dockerfiles |
| `infra.mdc` | CI, Railway, Vercel, Supabase, Upstash |
| `security.mdc` | Secrets, auth, validation |

## Non-negotiables

- Production-grade code; no placeholders unless requested
- Prisma schema at `prisma/schema.prisma`; API prefix `/api`
- Feature modules: `apps/api/src/features/`; infra: `apps/api/src/infrastructure/`
- Shared types: `@monolith/types`; shared UI: `@monolith/ui`
- PR gate: `pnpm lint`, `typecheck`, `test`, `build`, Playwright E2E

## Key paths

```
apps/api/src/features/     # Domain modules
apps/api/src/infrastructure/
apps/web/src/app/          # Next.js App Router
packages/types/            # API contracts
prisma/schema.prisma
infrastructure/docker/
.github/workflows/ci.yml
```
